reviewText:
There aren't hidden depths here, but it's still a fun ride.  Beautiful women, lust, love triangles, and dramatic music.  There are a lot of gaps in the plot, but the extensive disrobing makes up for it.

Enjoy it on its own terms.
Four women appear nude. Two give full frontals and the other two are topless only

You are in the midst of little twisty passages, all the same.  You are in the midst of twisting little passages all different...  Oh my the surprises in the well-turned plot make up for the abject nudity.
Not worth spending a lot of time watching but somewhat entertaining.
Held my attention.  Plot was solid, cast was pretty good.  In general, worth watching.
Crazy and true on what one would do for the passion and love one has for eachother. You forget about everything eles.
